snippet.title: MLB The Show 22 (Switch) - Gameplay
snippet.description: This is a full game of the Nintendo Switch version of MLB The Show 22. Colorado Rockies at Milwaukee Brewers. The game's totally playable on Switch but that framerate is not ideal.
